### 🧪 Tests API MemoLib - Collection Complète
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5078
@token = {{login.response.body.token}}

### ============================================
### 🔐 AUTHENTICATION
### ============================================

### 1. Register - Inscription nouvel utilisateur
# @name register
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@memolib.com",
  "password": "Test123!@#",
  "name": "Maître Test",
  "role": "AGENT",
  "phone": "+33612345678",
  "firmName": "Cabinet Test",
  "barNumber": "P12345",
  "address": "123 Rue Test",
  "city": "Paris",
  "postalCode": "75001",
  "plan": "CABINET"
}

### 2. Login - Connexion
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@memolib.com",
  "password": "Test123!@#"
}

### 3. Validate Token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/validate
Content-Type: application/json

"{{token}}"

### 4. Get Current User
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Change Password
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/change-password
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "Test123!@#",
  "newPassword": "NewTest123!@#"
}

### ============================================
### 📁 CASE MANAGEMENT
### ============================================

### 6. Create Case - Création dossier
# @name createCase
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/cases
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Dossier OQTF - Sophie Dubois",
  "description": "OQTF notifiée le 15/01/2026 avec délai de 30 jours",
  "clientEmail": "sophie.dubois@email.com",
  "clientName": "Sophie Dubois",
  "clientPhone": "+33612345678",
  "status": "OPEN",
  "priority": 5,
  "tags": ["OQTF", "urgent", "famille"],
  "dueDate": "2026-02-14T23:59:59Z"
}

### 7. Get All Cases
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cases
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Get Case by ID
@caseId = {{createCase.response.body.id}}
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cases/{{caseId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Get Case Timeline
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cases/{{caseId}}/timeline
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. Update Case Status
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/cases/{{caseId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "IN_PROGRESS",
  "comment": "Début du traitement du dossier"
}

### 11. Assign Case
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/cases/{{caseId}}/assign
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "assignedTo": "jean.dupont@cabinet-dupont.fr",
  "comment": "Attribution à Maître Dupont"
}

### 12. Update Case Tags
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/cases/{{caseId}}/tags
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tags": ["OQTF", "urgent", "famille", "recours"],
  "comment": "Ajout tag recours"
}

### 13. Update Case Priority
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/cases/{{caseId}}/priority
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "priority": 5,
  "dueDate": "2026-02-14T23:59:59Z",
  "comment": "Priorité maximale - délai légal"
}

### 14. Filter Cases
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cases/filter?status=OPEN&priority=5&tag=urgent
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 👥 CLIENT MANAGEMENT
### ============================================

### 15. Create Client
# @name createClient
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/client
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "mehdi.benamar@email.com",
  "name": "Mehdi Benamar",
  "phone": "+33698765432",
  "address": "45 Avenue de la République",
  "city": "Lyon",
  "postalCode": "69003",
  "notes": "Client régulier - renouvellement titre de séjour"
}

### 16. Get All Clients
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/client
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 17. Get Client Detail
@clientId = {{createClient.response.body.id}}
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/client/{{clientId}}/detail
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 18. Update Client
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/client/{{clientId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "mehdi.benamar@email.com",
  "name": "Mehdi Benamar",
  "phone": "+33698765432",
  "address": "45 Avenue de la République",
  "city": "Lyon",
  "postalCode": "69003",
  "notes": "Client VIP - renouvellement titre de séjour"
}

### ============================================
### 📧 EMAIL MANAGEMENT
### ============================================

### 19. Ingest Email
# @name ingestEmail
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ingest/email
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "from": "sophie.dubois@email.com",
  "to": "jean.dupont@cabinet-dupont.fr",
  "subject": "URGENT - OQTF notifiée le 15/01/2026",
  "body": "Bonjour Maître,\n\nJ'ai reçu une OQTF le 15/01/2026 avec un délai de départ volontaire de 30 jours.\n\nJe suis en France depuis 5 ans avec mes deux enfants scolarisés.\n\nMerci pour votre aide.",
  "messageId": "test-{{$timestamp}}@simulator.local",
  "receivedAt": "{{$datetime iso8601}}"
}

### 20. Send Email
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/email/send
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "to": "sophie.dubois@email.com",
  "subject": "Re: OQTF notifiée",
  "body": "Bonjour Madame Dubois,\n\nJ'ai bien reçu votre demande. Je vous propose un rendez-vous cette semaine.\n\nCordialement,\nMaître Dupont",
  "caseId": "{{caseId}}"
}

### 21. Create Email Template
# @name createTemplate
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/email/templates
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Confirmation RDV",
  "subject": "Confirmation de rendez-vous - {{clientName}}",
  "body": "Bonjour {{clientName}},\n\nVotre rendez-vous est confirmé pour le {{date}} à {{time}}.\n\nCordialement,\n{{lawyerName}}",
  "variables": ["clientName", "date", "time", "lawyerName"]
}

### 22. Get All Templates
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/email/templates
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 23. Manual Email Scan
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/email-scan/manual
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 24. Get Email Scan Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/email-scan/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 🔍 SEARCH
### ============================================

### 25. Text Search
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/search/events
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "OQTF",
  "limit": 10
}

### 26. Embeddings Search
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/embeddings/search
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "recours contentieux OQTF",
  "limit": 5
}

### 27. Semantic Search
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/semantic/search
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "dossiers urgents avec délai légal",
  "limit": 10
}

### ============================================
### 📎 ATTACHMENTS
### ============================================

### 28. Upload Attachment
@eventId = {{ingestEmail.response.body.eventId}}
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/attachment/upload/{{eventId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

<@test-document.pdf
------WebKitFormBoundary--

### 29. Get Attachments by Event
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/attachment/event/{{eventId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 📊 DASHBOARD & ANALYTICS
### ============================================

### 30. Get Dashboard Stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 31. Get Recent Activity
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/recent-activity
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 32. Get Alerts
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/alerts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 🔔 NOTIFICATIONS
### ============================================

### 33. Get Notifications
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 34. Mark Notification as Read
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/mark-read/{{notificationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 35. Mark All Notifications as Read
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/mark-all-read
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 👨💼 TEAM MANAGEMENT
### ============================================

### 36. Get Team Members
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/team/members
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 37. Invite Team Member
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/team/invite
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "collaborateur@cabinet-dupont.fr",
  "name": "Jean Collaborateur",
  "role": "COLLABORATOR"
}

### ============================================
### 💰 BILLING
### ============================================

### 38. Get Invoices
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/billing/invoices
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 39. Create Invoice
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/billing/invoices
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "clientId": "{{clientId}}",
  "caseId": "{{caseId}}",
  "amount": 1500.00,
  "description": "Recours contentieux OQTF",
  "dueDate": "2026-03-15T23:59:59Z"
}

### 40. Get Time Entries
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/billing/time-entries
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 41. Add Time Entry
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/billing/time-entries
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "caseId": "{{caseId}}",
  "duration": 120,
  "description": "Préparation recours contentieux",
  "date": "{{$datetime iso8601}}"
}

### ============================================
### 📅 CALENDAR
### ============================================

### 42. Get Calendar Events
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/calendar/events
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 43. Create Calendar Event
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/calendar/events
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "RDV Sophie Dubois",
  "description": "Consultation dossier OQTF",
  "startDate": "2026-01-25T10:00:00Z",
  "endDate": "2026-01-25T11:00:00Z",
  "caseId": "{{caseId}}",
  "location": "Cabinet"
}

### ============================================
### 🔒 SECURITY & AUDIT
### ============================================

### 44. Get Audit Log
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/audit?limit=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 45. Get Active Sessions
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/security/sessions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 🌐 SHARED WORKSPACE
### ============================================

### 46. Create Shared Workspace
# @name createWorkspace
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/shared-workspace/create
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Espace Client - Sophie Dubois",
  "description": "Espace de partage pour le dossier OQTF",
  "caseId": "{{caseId}}",
  "expiresAt": "2026-12-31T23:59:59Z",
  "allowedEmails": ["sophie.dubois@email.com"]
}

### 47. Access Shared Workspace (Public)
@workspaceToken = {{createWorkspace.response.body.token}}
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/shared-workspace/{{workspaceToken}}

### ============================================
### 🤖 AUTOMATIONS
### ============================================

### 48. Get Automations
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/automations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 49. Create Automation
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/automations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Auto-notification OQTF",
  "trigger": "EMAIL_RECEIVED",
  "conditions": [
    {
      "field": "subject",
      "operator": "contains",
      "value": "OQTF"
    }
  ],
  "actions": [
    {
      "type": "CREATE_CASE",
      "priority": 5
    },
    {
      "type": "SEND_NOTIFICATION",
      "message": "Nouveau dossier OQTF urgent"
    }
  ]
}

### ============================================
### 📊 REPORTS & EXPORT
### ============================================

### 50. Generate Report
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/generate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "MONTHLY_ACTIVITY",
  "startDate": "2026-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "endDate": "2026-01-31T23:59:59Z",
  "format": "PDF"
}

### 51. Export Cases
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/export/cases?format=csv&status=OPEN
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 🧪 HEALTH CHECK
### ============================================

### 52. Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### 53. API Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/status
